            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your<strong> cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Grate your<strong> Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
