    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the heated tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and add your <strong>pizza bases</strong></p><p>Divide the <strong>creamy tomato sauce</strong> between the pizza bases and spread it evenly all over them with the back of a spoon</p><p>Top with the <strong>grated cheddar</strong>, <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and<strong> torn mozzarella</strong></p><p>Dollop the<strong> remaining soft cheese </strong>evenly on top, then sprinkle the <strong>remaining dried oregano</strong> all over</p>",
