    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pizzas are cooking, remove the base of your<strong> lettuce</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>lettuce</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> and cut away the core, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the<strong> lettuce leaves </strong>from the stem until you are left with a pile of leaves</p>",
