      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> four-cheese pizza</strong> with the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> to the side</p><p>Top the salad with the <strong>roasted tomatoes</strong> and drizzle the <strong>tomato juices</strong> all over</p><p>Garnish the pizza with a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
